      <odd id="aspace_3a814239e46e813c027fa02d2cee6f0a">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 39-B (YRG 39-B), Records documenting specific religious denominations or groups at Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_c0c186209f33245b3ca20a365e376f2a">
